32:57.209 --> 32:58.709
Now, that's progress.

32:58.777 --> 33:00.877
I think you have to try
to be more helpful

33:00.946 --> 33:03.146
in pushing her to the forefront.

33:03.215 --> 33:04.848
ANNA: Some things
I disagree with you.

33:04.917 --> 33:06.283
I think that like I said
to you...

33:06.352 --> 33:08.552
LEMONIS: Some things you
disagree with or most things?

33:08.620 --> 33:10.387
It's still Susana's business.

33:10.456 --> 33:12.122
That's still the name
of the company.

33:12.191 --> 33:13.724
ANNA: I talk over people,
but it's not on purpose.

33:13.792 --> 33:14.825
I'm not trying
to be disrespectful.

33:14.893 --> 33:16.226
You know what I mean,

33:16.295 --> 33:17.661
sometimes it's just like...
LEMONIS: Tell her that.

33:17.730 --> 33:18.829
ANNA: Yes, and she knows
that sometimes I have an idea

33:18.897 --> 33:20.330
and I just have
to say something.

33:20.399 --> 33:21.465
SUSANA: No, but it
is disrespectful.

33:21.533 --> 33:22.632
This is something
that you do all the time.

33:22.701 --> 33:23.734
ANNA: I'm sorry
it's disrespectful to you,

33:23.802 --> 33:25.302
but I did not mean
to be disrespectful.

33:25.371 --> 33:27.170
Maybe I can be more mindful
about it

33:27.239 --> 33:28.839
and change this, you know.

33:28.907 --> 33:32.142
LEMONIS: Okay, well,
should be a great show.

33:32.211 --> 33:36.013
So you need to get your head
around being at the front.

33:40.886 --> 33:42.519
With the core collection
finalized,

33:42.588 --> 33:44.988
