to build the inventory

33:45.057 --> 33:46.256
so that retailers

33:46.325 --> 33:48.058
can get those items
all year long.

33:48.127 --> 33:49.259
But more importantly,

33:49.328 --> 33:51.928
the fashion show
is quickly approaching.

33:51.997 --> 33:54.798
And what I want Susana to do
is to focus on that

33:54.867 --> 33:56.433
and getting
the Spring line done.

33:56.502 --> 33:58.068
Susana.
SUSANA: Hey, Marcus.

33:58.137 --> 33:59.569
How's it going?
LEMONIS: Good.

33:59.638 --> 34:01.972
I wanted to check in
on the drawings

34:02.041 --> 34:03.273
for the new collection.

34:03.342 --> 34:05.909
Have you historically
had products this long?

34:05.978 --> 34:08.911
SUSANA: Um, not generally.

34:08.981 --> 34:10.313
LEMONIS: But what
prompted you to do that?

34:10.382 --> 34:13.183
SUSANA: Because the fabric
has a really great drape.

34:13.252 --> 34:15.518
It's got a really great hand.
