34:15.587 --> 34:17.754
because I'd like to see
some of the colors.

34:17.822 --> 34:20.223
Susana spends a lot of time
and money

34:20.292 --> 34:21.792
printing out different designs,

34:21.860 --> 34:23.659
and so I went out and I
bought her a new Epson printer.

34:23.728 --> 34:25.027
It doesn't have a cartridge.

34:25.097 --> 34:27.496
And it's mobile. You can move it
all around the office.

34:27.565 --> 34:30.132
Not only is the color vibrant,

34:30.202 --> 34:31.635
but it also comes
with an eco-tank

34:31.703 --> 34:33.036
and up to two years'
worth of ink,

34:33.105 --> 34:34.504
