a ton of money.

34:34.572 --> 34:35.906
You know how you buy
a printer and you're like,

34:35.974 --> 34:38.175
"I spend more on cartridges
than I did the printer."

34:38.243 --> 34:39.376
SUSANA: The colors
came out really great,

34:39.445 --> 34:40.476
and it's fast, too.

34:40.545 --> 34:42.012
LEMONIS: I love it.
SUSANA: Yeah.

34:42.081 --> 34:45.081
LEMONIS: I thought the three
of us could just spend a minute

34:45.150 --> 34:47.317
chatting and find out
how things have been going.

34:47.386 --> 34:51.922
SUSANA: I want to be partners,
but not in the terms of her

34:51.989 --> 34:54.324
telling me
what to do in my own business.

34:54.393 --> 34:56.159
ANNA: I'm not bossing
anybody around,

34:56.228 --> 34:57.394
because it's her company.

34:57.463 --> 34:58.695
If it's her company and it means

34:58.764 --> 35:00.397
that she doesn't need
to produce line on time,

35:00.466 --> 35:01.698
that it bothers me,
you understand?

35:01.767 --> 35:03.667
If she doesn't like my opinion,
okay, fine, but...

35:03.735 --> 35:05.735
SUSANA: I don't like when you
have this impression,

35:05.804 --> 35:07.104
"Well, she..."

35:07.172 --> 35:08.805
This kind of sort of push me
on the side kind of thing.

35:08.874 --> 35:10.273
I don't like it.

35:10.342 --> 35:14.478
I have to be able to say
my opinion and say what I feel.

35:14.546 --> 35:17.547
I'm the owner of the company.
My name's on the door.

35:17.616 --> 35:19.683
LEMONIS: I just feel like this
is gonna continue for years.

35:19.751 --> 35:20.917
How does this resolve itself?

35:20.986 --> 35:22.385
SUSANA: I don't know.
LEMONIS: Do you want

35:22.454 --> 35:24.387
Anna to be part
of the company going forward?

35:24.456 --> 35:26.857
SUSANA: If there's a change.
If there's a change, yes.

35:26.925 --> 35:29.392
If there's not a change, then
we can, you know, part ways.

35:29.461 --> 35:31.895
ANNA: She cannot face
things by herself.

35:31.964 --> 35:33.163
SUSANA:
Can you please shut up?

35:33.232 --> 35:35.198
I just want to clean this up,
do you understand?

35:35.267 --> 35:37.534
ANNA: Instead of waiting for you
to say all those things

35:37.603 --> 35:39.269
she told me she wouldn't,
you know what I mean?

35:39.338 --> 35:40.370
She would have had
this conversation...

35:40.439 --> 35:41.671
SUSANA: 'Cause you know why?
I'm done.

35:41.740 --> 35:43.373
I'm done with this relationship,
how we work.

35:43.442 --> 35:44.574
I'm done with it.

35:47.412 --> 35:48.745
LEMONIS: This is a big night.
SUSANA: Yeah.

35:48.814 --> 35:49.946
LEMONIS: Have you seen
how many people are up there?

35:50.015 --> 35:51.781
SUSANA: No.
LEMONIS: "Allure's" there.

35:51.850 --> 35:54.518
"Vanity Fair's" there.
It's packed.

35:58.490 --> 36:00.123
ANNA: She cannot face
things by herself.

36:00.192 --> 36:01.458
She could not talk...

36:01.527 --> 36:02.459
SUSANA: What do you mean
face things by yourself?

36:02.528 --> 36:03.660
You know why?
I'm done.

36:03.729 --> 36:05.328
I'm done with this relationship,
how we work.

36:05.397 --> 36:06.796
I'm done with it.
LEMONIS: Do you guys

36:06.865 --> 36:09.332
realize that the two of you
really argue about nothing?

36:09.401 --> 36:11.735
ANNA: Sometimes, you know,
I can be aggressive,

36:11.803 --> 36:13.136
and I do get upset.

36:13.205 --> 36:15.138
SUSANA: I want it to work.
I've always wanted it to work,

36:15.207 --> 36:16.439
but there has to be
mutual respect.

36:16.508 --> 36:17.574
That's what needs to happen.

36:17.643 --> 36:18.842
LEMONIS: We have
a big presentation.

36:18.911 --> 36:20.177
I'm excited about it.

36:20.245 --> 36:21.945
I've spent a lot of money.

36:22.014 --> 36:24.814
Do you think you guys
can work together?

36:24.883 --> 36:26.149
SUSANA: I think
we can work together.

36:26.218 --> 36:29.085
LEMONIS: Do you think
you can work together?

36:29.154 --> 36:31.555
ANNA: Yep.

36:35.627 --> 36:37.827
LEMONIS: It's a busy time
at Susana Monaco.

36:37.896 --> 36:42.098
I've invested $100,000
into creating the new core line

36:42.167 --> 36:43.733
and building up the inventory.

36:43.802 --> 36:45.569
And in just a few days,
we're gonna be

36:45.637 --> 36:48.205
