37:19.404 --> 37:21.705
LEMONIS: Just a couple
more details to iron out,

37:21.773 --> 37:22.906
and we should be good to go.

37:22.975 --> 37:24.975
Nice.
Really nice.

37:25.043 --> 37:26.843
I think the collection
looks great.

37:35.454 --> 37:37.520
Today we're gonna be
having the fashion show.

37:37.589 --> 37:42.626
I invited bloggers and editors
and buyers to create a buzz.

37:45.030 --> 37:47.397
Fashion show is
a different form of marketing

37:47.466 --> 37:49.032
that not only puts

37:49.101 --> 37:52.269
Susana Monaco's new line
on display,

37:52.337 --> 37:54.838
but hopefully it puts Susana
on display, as well.

