And I spent a lot of money
putting on this show.

38:15.193 --> 38:16.660
But what's more
important to me

38:16.728 --> 38:19.029
is that I want to see Susana
getting out in front of people,

38:19.097 --> 38:21.398
being proud of her work
and who she is.

38:21.466 --> 38:23.767
SUSANA: Everybody has to stand.
This is standing.

38:23.835 --> 38:25.669
This is power position.

38:25.737 --> 38:27.771
Shoulders back.

38:27.839 --> 38:30.173
You own this.

38:30.242 --> 38:33.410
LEMONIS: This is a perfect night
for you to get a fresh start.

38:33.478 --> 38:35.045
Tonight's about Susana.
