LEMONIS: But, Anna,
don't let your attitude get

38:44.156 --> 38:45.322
in the way of your talent.

38:45.390 --> 38:46.323
ANNA: No, no, no.
LEMONIS: Do we have a deal?

38:46.391 --> 38:47.724
ANNA: Yes.

38:47.793 --> 38:49.459
LEMONIS: Let's get back in there
and support her, okay?

38:51.863 --> 38:54.197
SUSANA: All right, ladies,
let me take a look, please.

38:57.569 --> 38:59.536
