MARIO: If anybody need help,
I can do this.

39:05.477 --> 39:07.243
LEMONIS:
Ladies look amazing.

39:07.312 --> 39:08.745
This is a big night.
SUSANA: Yeah.

39:08.814 --> 39:10.180
LEMONIS: This is like
the rebirth.

39:10.248 --> 39:11.848
SUSANA: It's crazy.

39:11.917 --> 39:13.450
LEMONIS:
What's crazy about it?

