39:47.452 --> 39:49.619
LEMONIS: This is where you were
always meant to be.

39:49.688 --> 39:50.687
SUSANA: Yay.

39:50.756 --> 39:52.522
Very exciting.
Let's have a show.

39:52.591 --> 39:54.758
Come on!
Whoo!

39:56.862 --> 39:58.361
LEMONIS: Folks,
it's a big night.

39:58.430 --> 39:59.829
I have the pleasure of being

39:59.898 --> 40:02.866
a new partner in a business
called Susana Monaco.

