Tonight, we're gonna be

40:04.369 --> 40:06.803
showing you
a brand-new collection

40:06.872 --> 40:08.938
that Susana has
designed herself,

40:09.007 --> 40:13.543
and it is the Spring/Summer
collection for 2017.

40:16.314 --> 40:18.281
The new Spring line
is manufactured

40:18.350 --> 40:20.350
with high quality supplex,

40:20.419 --> 40:23.653
