in the core collection.

40:29.294 --> 40:31.161
But it all starts with the buzz
we get created today.

40:31.229 --> 40:32.896
Don't shake.
It's okay.

40:32.964 --> 40:34.931
This is what you worked for.
SUSANA: Yeah.

