41:20.579 --> 41:21.945
that we went through
that whole process,

41:22.013 --> 41:23.213
and I think
they're getting past it.

41:23.281 --> 41:25.048
LEMONIS: And with
the manufacturing process

41:25.116 --> 41:26.749
for this line
going off without a hitch,

41:26.818 --> 41:29.118
well, it shows me that
real progress is being made.

41:30.922 --> 41:34.290
SUSANA:
She's a confident, chic,

41:34.359 --> 41:35.859
a strong woman who feels
good about herself.

41:35.927 --> 41:38.027
LEMONIS: So you'll be able
to buy it at Bloomingdale's,

41:38.096 --> 41:39.562
Nordstrom, Saks,

41:39.631 --> 41:42.632
Rue La La,
Susanamonaco.com, Shopbop.

41:42.701 --> 41:44.567
Throughout
my journey with Susana,

41:44.636 --> 41:46.803
I had one real goal in mind,

41:46.872 --> 41:48.872
and that was seeing
Susana comfortable

41:48.940 --> 41:51.207
with putting herself
at the forefront.

41:51.276 --> 41:53.076
People like to buy
from people.

41:53.144 --> 41:55.178
Now that she's not
hiding anymore,

41:55.247 --> 41:58.481
her sales are starting to follow
that same path of growth.

41:58.550 --> 42:00.149
I think the sky's the limit.

42:00.218 --> 42:01.251
ANNA: Congrats.

42:01.319 --> 42:02.485
SUSANA: Thank you so much.

42:05.156 --> 42:06.356
ANNA: You know
we do love each other.

42:06.424 --> 42:07.490
SUSANA: Yes.

