42:09.461 --> 42:11.928
ANNA: Yeah.

42:11.997 --> 42:13.162
LEMONIS:
I'm very proud of you.

42:13.231 --> 42:14.531
SUSANA: Thank you
so much, Marcus.

42:14.599 --> 42:16.099
LEMONIS: You know,
one thing that I think

42:16.167 --> 42:18.601
is important for you to remember

42:18.670 --> 42:20.436
is that you can't lose
your backbone anymore.

42:20.505 --> 42:22.572
SUSANA: No.
I think this whole experience

42:22.641 --> 42:26.409
has been an incredible
turning point, a change.

42:26.478 --> 42:29.779
It's not gonna go back.
LEMONIS: Good luck.

